speech.p:
asked the President of the Board of Trade (1) what information he has as to the number of British firms which have indicated an intention of participating in the Canadian International Trade Fair to be held next May;

(2) what incentives or assistance have been offered to British manufacturers to participate in the Canadian International Trade Fair in May;

what has been done to direct the attention of British industries to the possibilities offered by the Canadian International Trade Fair which he is to open in Toronto on 28th May next.
